2) Brutal critical evaluation

What‚Äôs genuinely strong

Intent-preservation with locked entities: this is the defensible core. If you claim it as a decoding-time constraint mechanism (not just ‚Äúwe check facts‚Äù), it becomes technically specific and hard to clone. 

