Clear, simple story for users and buyers (‚Äúempathy autocorrect,‚Äù ‚Äústops you from shooting yourself in the foot‚Äù). 


Real risks / blind spots

Over-specific claim numerics (weights, ‚Äú<200 ms,‚Äù ‚Äú<50 MB,‚Äù ‚Äú>85% similarity‚Äù). These are fragile in prosecution and discovery. Put numbers in spec or performance targets, not in independent claims. Your provisional currently locks them in. 

Over-limiting ‚Äúall on-device‚Äù in independent claims. Great as posture; risky as claim requirement. Make on-device a preferred embodiment / dependent claim so you can legally cover hybrid/local-first variants later. 

101 abstract-idea risk for Empathy Delta. A ‚Äúscore for communication quality‚Äù can be dismissed as a mental process/organizing human activity unless you anchor it to specific feature extraction, constrained decoding, and a concrete injection interface that alters computer operation. Your docs need more of that tie-down. 

